cutthecrap.utils.striterators

Interface IStriterator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Enumeration, Iterator
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IXPropertyIterator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Striterator, XPropertyIterator

    public interface IStriterator
extends Iterator, Enumeration
    Striterator - transformation and mapping patterns over java Iterator s.

    Extends the Iterator interface to expose methods to add IFilter objects and a specific Type filter
